task.summary: Default task
Implemented getIntVal and getDoubleVal methods for Number class
Corrected if statement for setting initial weight
Corrected revise method Added toString method

Changed eventTrigger's to accomodate for belief revision instead of belief addition/deletion
Made goals base term type Term instead of Belief as in AgentSpeak(L) paper
Updated action methods. Removed add/delete belief actions. Removed add/delete belief events. Deleted BeliefGoal class Added ReviseBeliefAction. Deleted Belief class.
Added toString methods
Implemented full parser that reads *.txt files and instantiates an interpreter.
Changed to double number
Changed internal event to AddGoalET
Added unify() methods
Made abstract
Implemented unification
Changed plan eventTrigger to type eventTrigger instead of event
Implemented unification
Made getGUB() method public
Implemented World class
Implemented parser for uncertain agentSpeak. Enabled txt file input.
Deleted superseeded and unnecessary files
Added exception to executeAction() method
Implemented substitute methods for all logical expressions

Changed BeliefBase to GlobalUncertainBelief
Implemented convertToNNF() and inNNF() methods for all LogicalExpressions
Added isGround() methods
Corrected revise method and getLambda
Implemented entailment. Added langaugeCotains function and getRelevantES() method
Added entials() method for just LogicalExpression input
Added toNNF check in getLambda() method
Changed bleief base to global uncertain belief
Implemented sat4J SATsolver
Implemented isClassical() method for Plausibility/Negation as failure
